"title": "3275: Holy Spirit, in the church",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "3275",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The church depends upon the activity of the Holy Spirit, without which its effective and faithful service is impossible.</p>\n<h2>The Holy Spirit forms the church</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:13\">1CO 12:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:1-Acts2:4\">ACT 2:1–2:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:16-Acts2:18\">ACT 2:16–2:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel2:28-Joel2:29\">JOL 2:28–2:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:44-Acts10:48\">ACT 10:44–10:48</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:21-Eph2:22\">EPH 2:21–2:22</a></p>\n<h2>The Holy Spirit indwells the church</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor3:16\">1CO 3:16</a></strong> <em>“you” here is plural and refers to the whole church.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek10:4\">EZK 10:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:14\">JHN 16:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:19\">1CO 6:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor6:16\">2CO 6:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:14\">1PE 4:14</a></p>\n<h2>The Holy Spirit enables the church to function as the body of Christ</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:7\">1CO 12:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod31:1-Exod31:5\">EXO 31:1–31:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num11:24-Num11:27\">NUM 11:24–11:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam10:5-1Sam10:11\">1SA 10:5–10:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:5\">ROM 12:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:8-1Cor12:11\">1CO 12:8–12:11</a></p>\n<h2>The Holy Spirit enables Christian unity</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:3-Eph4:4\">EPH 4:3–4:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:1\">PHP 2:1</a></p>\n<h2>The church worships, serves and speaks by the Holy Spirit</h2>\n<h3>The church worships by the Spirit</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:11\">ACT 2:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:24\">JHN 4:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:45-Acts10:46\">ACT 10:45–10:46</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:15\">ROM 8:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor14:26-1Cor14:33\">1CO 14:26–14:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:3\">PHP 3:3</a></p>\n<h3>The church serves by the Spirit</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:6-Rom12:8\">ROM 12:6–12:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:7-1Cor12:11\">1CO 12:7–12:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:7-Eph4:13\">EPH 4:7–4:13</a></p>\n<h3>The church speaks by the Spirit</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts6:10\">ACT 6:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:8\">ACT 4:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor14:24-1Cor14:25\">1CO 14:24–14:25</a></p>\n<h2>The Holy Spirit communicates Jesus Christ's message to the church</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:7\">REV 2:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:26\">JHN 14:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:13\">JHN 16:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:11\">REV 2:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:17\">REV 2:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:29\">REV 2:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:6\">REV 3:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:13\">REV 3:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:22\">REV 3:22</a></p>\n<h2>The Holy Spirit and the church's mission</h2>\n<h3>The church fulfils its mission by the Spirit</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:8\">ACT 1:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:26-John15:27\">JHN 15:26–15:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:21-John20:23\">JHN 20:21–20:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:31\">ACT 4:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:3\">GAL 3:3</a></p>\n<h3>The Spirit directs the church's missionary enterprise</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:2-Acts13:3\">ACT 13:2–13:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:28\">ACT 15:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:6\">ACT 16:6</a></p>",
